Freddie Prinze https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freddie_Prinze 0 Freddie James Prinze (born Frederick Karl Pruetzel; June 22, 1954 – January 29, 1977) was an American stand-up comedian and actor. Prinze was the star of NBC-TV sitcom Chico and the Man from 1974 until his death in 1977. Prinze is the father of actor Freddie Prinze Jr. Freddie_James_Prinze ( born Frederick_Karl_Pruetzel ; June_22_,_1954 – January_29_,_1977 ) was an_American_stand-up_comedian_and_actor .
